An Activation Function decides whether a neuron should produce output or not.

It is like a decision maker in a neural network.

=========

Simple Meaning

After ANN calculates:

Input × Weight + Bias

the activation function checks:

"Should this neuron activate?"

Then it gives final output.

========

Flow in ANN

Inputs
   ↓
Weights Applied
   ↓
Summation (Net Input)
   ↓
Activation Function
   ↓
Final Output

============







